Initalize using the default configuration
==========================================
repo init -u http://sw-stash.freescale.net/scm/alb/fsl-s32v-yocto-bsp.git
repo sync

Initialize using the latest manifest on the develop branch
==========================================================
repo init -u http://sw-stash.freescale.net/scm/alb/fsl-s32v-yocto-bsp.git -b develop
repo sync

Note: If targetting another branch, change the '-b' parameter accordingly.
